NDA-IPRA

A digital non-disclsure and intellectual property rights agreement generated and signed on mobile devices.

In the modern economy, it is difficult to share ideas with unkwown third-parties. An instantly-generated NDA-IPRA can protect a proprietor. 

Without legal contracts, it is hard to share proprietary information. 

This product protects intellectual property while facilitating sharing. NDA-IPRA generates a legal-document in a matter of moments that can then be signed on mobile devices. 

"I rest easier knowing my intellectual property is secure."

Download NDA-IPRA, select your IP, and obtain a signature.

"I can now speak about my IP with many people, knowing that I am legally protected."

NDA-IPRA can be obtained online.